---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="How taewoon.kim handles analytics, cookie choices, and direct contact.">
  <section class="section section--document">
    <header class="page-header page-header--simple">
      <h1>Privacy policy</h1>
      <p>How analytics, cookie choices, and information shared through this website are handled.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="prose prose--document">
      <h2>Website analytics</h2>
      <p>taewoon.kim uses Google Analytics only if you accept analytics cookies. If you accept, analytics is used only to understand aggregate website usage such as visited pages and general traffic patterns.</p>

      <h2>Cookie choices</h2>
      <p>You can accept or decline analytics cookies from the banner shown on first visit. You can reopen those choices later through the cookie settings link in the footer.</p>

      <h2>Direct contact</h2>
      <p>If you contact me directly by email or through linked channels, the information you provide is used only to respond to your message and continue the conversation you started.</p>

      <h2>Updates</h2>
      <p>This policy may be updated over time as the site, analytics setup, or contact workflows change.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>